---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Our Philosophy',
  description: 'The Match Bureau philosophy — private matchmaking for New Zealand\'s most discerning individuals. Quality over quantity. Discretion above all.',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <main transition:animate="fade">
    <header class="px-12 mb-32">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8">
          <span class="block text-[#cda777] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] mb-6">Introduction</span>
          <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-light text-[#eac290] leading-tight tracking-tight italic" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Our Philosophy</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 flex items-end">
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl italic text-[#9b8f82] leading-relaxed border-l border-[#4e453b] pl-8" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            In an era of algorithmic convenience, we defend the luxury of human intuition and the depth of private selection.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-40 px-12">
      <div class="w-full h-[716px] bg-[#161b2b] relative overflow-hidden">
        <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000" alt="Luxurious dark interior of a private library with leather chairs and warm amber lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDc-UVdUFszuciZOhnr8NiMd9FtEDd80C9-euyX-GQXpz-ctpWI01v18Jt-u1kEA5DuK_kWY_Q0S8Erzc2aoPOW3w3eN-ExY4_fmAp-NeqylG0Xqralb_O6salSTzGwqv31kwfpUCjQTICfcbePwv38Mk0eKBej-ZYsAgrWd_Y2JvsyzPVSUxA6xfzwAPPhwqley_cNZUyrvBeM_-x5rfJxCYf2JZi5-KJYXXSyR_ZoEXA0HLV6ZLzhmRVBwRscYPvMV6B5KMN4Q5fw" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0e1322] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-12 mb-40">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-16">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl text-[#cda777] mb-8" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Quality over Quantity</h2>
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-[#cda777] mb-8"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7 md:col-start-6">
          <p class="text-2xl text-[#dee1f7] leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            We reject the digital carousel of modern dating. Our approach is curated, deliberate, and finite. We do not offer a database to browse; we offer a singular focus on a select few who represent the pinnacle of compatibility.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-[#9b8f82] leading-relaxed max-w-xl" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
            At The Match Bureau, we believe that true connection requires the investment of time and the wisdom of experience. Our members are not profiles; they are legacies, personalities, and aspirations. We limit our active clientele to ensure every match is vetted with forensic precision.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#161b2b] py-40 px-12 mb-40">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 order-2 md:order-1">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-[#0e1322] relative">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 grayscale" alt="Gentleman in bespoke suit adjusting cufflinks" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBeLHzNKXoMoCero0m9eiZBhs-Vq7MJSw3nTSCIDcfJxu06HGHQwVRF0IteUhowZgzS8RTquGjeB90eWDPRhRhLy2V2a9K9d-GJrE7XCx_R8Qi5fphlL6Sgh9VRwyejgtWb6ddkW68SiM2mSVIH32MIEvs8WEIsrJFSU6I_qkkmXHDxRHM95qDNL4T6kx776a3ygUHr6rc7xcw4QG-jDb9EK_i3gUX-nzeBfyXAc-DyksvPASVET0wRm8dAbzlgG6yaxYS5vTd7qDT8" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7 order-1 md:order-2">
          <span class="text-[#cda777] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[10px] mb-8 block" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">The Discretion Promise</span>
          <h2 class="text-5xl text-[#eac290] mb-12 italic leading-tight" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Your life is private. <br/>Your search should be too.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-8 max-w-lg">
            <p class="text-xl italic text-[#dee1f7]" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
              "Discretion is not merely a policy; it is our foundational pillar."
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#9b8f82] leading-relaxed" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
              Our clients include high-profile executives, public figures, and industry leaders who value their anonymity above all. We operate entirely offline, ensuring no digital footprint of your personal search ever exists. Your identity is only revealed to a potential match once mutual interest and strict compatibility are established.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-12 mb-56">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-16">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 md:col-start-3 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-[#eac290] mb-16 tracking-tight" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">For whom it is intended</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 border-r border-[#4e453b] pr-12 text-right">
          <h3 class="uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-bold text-[#cda777] mb-6" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">The Successful</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-[#9b8f82] italic" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">For those who have mastered their professional worlds and now seek the same excellence in their personal lives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 text-center px-12">
          <h3 class="uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-bold text-[#cda777] mb-6" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">The Intuitive</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-[#9b8f82] italic" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">For those who understand that human chemistry cannot be reduced to an algorithm or a set of binary choices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 border-l border-[#4e453b] pl-12 text-left">
          <h3 class="uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-bold text-[#cda777] mb-6" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">The Discerning</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-[#9b8f82] italic" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">For those who value their time and refuse to settle for anything less than a profound, meaningful connection.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-12 mb-32">
      <div class="bg-[#161b2b] p-24 text-center border border-[#4e453b]">
        <h2 class="text-4xl text-[#eac290] mb-12 italic" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Begin the Conversation</h2>
        <p class="text-[#9b8f82] text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12" style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;">
          Membership is by application only. Every journey begins with a private consultation to understand your legacy and your vision for the future.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-[#cda777] text-[#573c15] px-12 py-5 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold hover:bg-[#eac290] transition-all inline-block" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">Request Invitation</a>
          <a href="/process" class="border border-[#9b8f82] text-[#cda777] px-12 py-5 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold hover:bg-[#cda777]/10 transition-all inline-block" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">View Process</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
